  <brief_title>A Study to Investigate the Pharmacokinetics of RO7223280 in Critically Ill Participants With Bacterial Infections</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Single-Dose, Uncontrolled, Open-label, One Group Study to Investigate the Pharmacokinetics of RO7223280 in Critically Ill Patients With Bacterial Infections</official_title>
