  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main aim of the study is to investigate the plasma pharmacokinetics (PK) and safety of&#xD;
      intravenous (IV) administration of a single dose of 600 mg RO7223280 in critically ill&#xD;
      participants with bacterial infections.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
